title: Dochinpira (The Gigolo: Dochinpira)
synopsis: Jin is one horny hunk, a twenty-two year old stud with lady killer looks. He's challenged by gorgeous Ai Mizushima to "make me scream with pleasure" it's a wager he can't refuse especially the when the prize is a brand new sports car.
